       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PROCESADOR-PAGO.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

       DATA DIVISION.

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       01 WS-TABLE-IN.
          05 WS-ITEM OCCURS 100 TIMES.
             10 WS-VALUE PIC 9(5) VALUE 0.

       01 WS-INDEX PIC 9(5) VALUE 0.
       01 WS-TABLE-INDE PIC 9(5) VALUE 0.

       01 WS-MESSAGE PIC X(50) VALUE "INIT".

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       MAIN-PARA.

           DISPLAY "=== INICIO PROCESADOR PAGO ==="

           MOVE 1 TO WS-INDEX

           PERFORM VARYING WS-INDEX FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-INDEX > 100

               MOVE WS-INDEX TO WS-TABLE-INDE
               MOVE WS-INDEX TO WS-ITEM(WS-INDEX)

           END-PERFORM

           MOVE "PROCESAMIENTO OK" TO WS-MESSAGE

           DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE

           DISPLAY "=== FIN PROCESADOR PAGO ==="

           STOP RUN.
